title: Dancing With Myself (feat. Robert Kelly)
description:
Robert Kelly joins Big Jay Oakerson and expresses his immense hatred for the whole concept of dance. Jay takes Bobby through the musical numbers on a public access show that just happened to include some very brave dancing.
